perfcenter.baseclass

Class Host

  • java.lang.Object
    • perfcenter.baseclass.Host
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    HostSim

    public class Host
extends java.lang.Object
    This represents the host definition in the input file. A host can have software servers deployed onto them. Host has set of devices and an host is deployed on to a single LAN. Host also has virtual resources and devices deployed on them.
    Author:
    akhila, rakesh, bhavin
